B.rV=new A.nV("Urban Warmth","25-35, confident urban professionals who value authenticity","Full-bleed impact meets organic approachability. This design puts the photo front and center as the hero element, combining the bold condensed typography of street culture with the warm earth tones and organic shapes of natural design. The result is confident yet inviting \u2014 a dating profile that feels both impactful and genuine.","Bebas Neue","Lato",B.a2N,B.Tb,'The full-bleed photo makes an immediate emotional connection \u2014 you see the person, not a UI. The warm terracotta gradient overlay feels inviting rather than moody. Bebas Neue display type adds confidence and urban edge without feeling aggressive. Sage green verified badge and organic pills soften the boldness beautifully. This is the "less is more" approach done right.',"Full-bleed designs depend heavily on photo quality \u2014 a poorly lit selfie will look worse here than in a card-based layout with padding and decoration. The warm overlay tints all photos with terracotta, which may not suit every skin tone. Less visual structure means less room for detailed profile information.")
